reviewText:
What a rip off. I ordered it and got some Queens &  Kings of storytelling on one DVD and no one did a Paul Laurence Dunbar poem!
The 2nd DVD had only audio files that could only be played on computer! And again, nothing about Dunbar! The label on the 2nd DVD even had my name listed as one of the performers and its wasn't a DVD...only a AUDIO. I WAS proud to be a part of this production but now I'm embarrassed!
